        "## Introduction\n",
        "\n",
        "This file demonstrates the three primary ways to create collapsible folds inside a Quarto document.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 1. Native Code Folding\n",
        "\n",
        "Below is a Python code chunk that is folded by default."
      ],
      "id": "d42fb988"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
